: 568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are the most common ones that Portuguese travelers need to be wary of: Perhaps the most widespread scam, Olympic ticket fraud, involves the sale of counterfeit tickets.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999892413662871, \"rank\": 6.683303977217029e-06, \"text\": \"Portuguese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most common ones\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"Perhaps the most widespread scam\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic ticket fraud\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"the sale\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"counterfeit tickets\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scammers create convincing websites that mimic official ticketing platforms.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Scammers\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"convincing websites\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The websites look legit, but they are designed to steal your credit card information.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The websites\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"legit\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"your credit card information\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One red flag you may notice is that they offer seats at heavily discounted prices.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One red flag\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"seats\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"heavily discounted prices\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The scam site may promise guaranteed tickets, even when games are sold out.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The scam site\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"guaranteed tickets\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you take this bait, you will end up having worthless tickets and will not be able to get your money back.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this bait\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"worthless tickets\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"your money\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many fans wish to own a piece of Olympic memorabilia.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many fans\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"a piece\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic memorabilia\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They often order shirts, hats, or photos to celebrate the event.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"shirts\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"hats\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The desire to own a piece of the Olympics can also make fans vulnerable to merchandise scams.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The desire\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"a piece\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"merchandise scams\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cybercriminals can set up fake websites or social media pages to sell \\\"official\\\" merchandise.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cybercriminals\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"fake websites\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"social media pages\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"official\\\" merchandise\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prices are typically heavily discounted on fake merchandise websites.\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Prices\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"fake merchandise websites\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once you order, you may never receive the item or get a cheap, poorly made product instead.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the item\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"a cheap, poorly made product\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As fans flock to Paris from Portugal, scammers offer enticing deals for travel packages or accommodations.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1734, \"end\": 1739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.3170854779956184e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"score\": 0.9998069597118423, \"rank\": 0.0001395943611254774, \"text\": \"Portugal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"scammers\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"enticing deals\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"travel packages\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"accommodations\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The counterfeit companies may ask for upfront payment and not provide any actual bookings.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The counterfeit companies\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"upfront payment\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"any actual bookings\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you fall victim to this type of scam, you may end up stranded and unable to reach your destination.\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"victim\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"this type\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"scam\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"your destination\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To ensure your Olympic experience remains fun, consider the following best practices: Always rely on official sources when purchasing tickets, merchandise, or booking travel.The Paris 2024 Olympics websiteis a good place to start if you plan to travel for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your Olympic experience\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"the following best practices\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"official sources\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2138}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"merchandise\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"a good place\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It offers authorized links to buy tickets, make travel arrangements, and order gear.\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"authorized links\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"travel arrangements\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"order gear\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you use a third-party seller, research their online reputation.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a third-party seller\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"their online reputation\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Check out any reviews and verify that the website is legitimate.\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any reviews\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"the website\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Customer feedback can reveal if there is anything suspicious about the seller.\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Customer feedback\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"the seller\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Use payment methods that offer fraud protection, like credit cards, whenever possible.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"payment methods\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"fraud protection\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"credit cards\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you become a scam victim, you may dispute the charges and hopefully recover the lost money.\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a scam victim\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"the charges\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2733}, {\"ngram\": \"the lost money\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not engage in emails, phone calls, or social media messages asking for personal information, like financial details.\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"emails\", \"fro