, \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3210}, {\"ngram\": \"your online activities\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3253}, {\"ngram\": \"financial transactions\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3285}, {\"ngram\": \"your trip\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3303}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using a VPN while traveling to the Paris Olympics offers several advantages, including: A VPN masks your IP address and encrypts your data in transit, making it difficult for internet service providers, advertisers, or third parties to track your online activities.\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3430, \"end\": 3440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.990546457863877e-26, \"text\": \"IP address\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a VPN\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3373}, {\"ngram\": \"several advantages\", \"from\": 3381, \"to\": 3399}, {\"ngram\": \"your data\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3462}, {\"ngram\": \"transit\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3473}, {\"ngram\": \"internet service providers\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"advertisers\", \"from\": 3527, \"to\": 3538}, {\"ngram\": \"third parties\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3556}, {\"ngram\": \"your online activities\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Access to specific websites and online services may be restricted or censored in some countries.\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Access\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3598}, {\"ngram\": \"specific websites\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3619}, {\"ngram\": \"online services\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3639}, {\"ngram\": \"some countries\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A VPN can help you bypass these geo-restrictions.\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A VPN\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3694}, {\"ngram\": \"these geo-restrictions\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While in Paris, you can still visit your favorite social media sites, news outlets, and streaming services.\", \"from\": 3739, \"to\": 3846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3748, \"end\": 3753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.3170854779956184e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your favorite social media sites\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3807}, {\"ngram\": \"news outlets\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3821}, {\"ngram\": \"streaming services\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Public Wi-Fi hotspots available around the Olympics will be an attraction point to hackers.\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3939, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Public Wi-Fi hotspots\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3869}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3899}, {\"ngram\": \"an attraction point\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 3927}, {\"ngram\": \"hackers\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 3938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since a VPN encrypts your internet traffic, your login details, financial information, and other data will remain protected from the snoopers online.\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 4089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a VPN\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3951}, {\"ngram\": \"your internet traffic\", \"from\": 3961, \"to\": 3982}, {\"ngram\": \"your login details\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 4002}, {\"ngram\": \"financial information\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4025}, {\"ngram\": \"other data\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4041}, {\"ngram\": \"the snoopers\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prices for flight